result:
div
  .padding-large(style="height: 100%")
    div
      h2 Bookings
    div.margin-y
    
      div.card.padding.flex.justify-space-between.align-center.margin-bottom-small(v-for="booking in $store.getters.myBookings")
        div.flex
          div
            h5 DATE
            br
            span {{booking.booking_date}}
          div.margin-left-large
            h5 STATUS
            br
            span {{booking.booking_status}}
        div
          button(@click=`$refs.booking.show(booking)`) View Details

  modal(ref="booking" inline-template)
    form(@submit.prevent="")
      transition(name='fade' appear)
        #backdrop.fixed-fill(@click="toggle" v-show="visible")
      transition(name='center-scale' appear)
        #modal(v-show="visible").card.fixed-center.flex.column.five-large.seven-medium.twelve-small.max-high
          div.flex.justify-space-between.align-center.wide
            h2.padding Booking Details
            a.padding(@click="toggle"): fa(icon='times')
          hr
          div.padding.overflow-auto
            table.wide
              tr
                td Schedule
                td {{params.booking_date}}
              tr
                td Status
                td {{params.booking_status}}
              tr
                td Total Price
                td {{params.booking_total_price}}
              tr
                td Payment Slip
                td
                  fileupload(ref="fileupload")
            form()
                fieldset
                  details
                    summary Package Details
                    br
                    table.wide
                      tr
                        td Package Name
                        td {{ JSON.parse(params.package).package_name }}
                      tr
                        td Package Description
                        td {{ JSON.parse(params.package)['package_description'] }}
                      tr
                        td Duration
                        td {{ JSON.parse(params.package)['package_minutes'] }}
                      tr
                        td Addons
                        td
                          ul
                            li(v-for="addon in JSON.parse(params.booking_addons)")
                              span {{addon.addon_type}} : {{addon.addon_description}} (P {{addon.addon_price}})
                      tr
                        td Themes
                        td
                          ul
                              li(v-for="themeid in JSON.parse(params.booking_themes)")
                                span {{themeid}}

            br
            div.flex
              button.flex-grow(type="submit" v-if="params.booking_status=='AWAITING_PAYMENT'" @click="$parent.submitPayment(params.booking_id); visible=false") Submit Payment
